title: Evacuees jam Marysville gas stations
text: Evacuees jam Marysville gas stations Feb 12, 2017 Concerned citizens in Marysville, California are not waiting around to see what happens with the Oroville Dam spillway, but are gathering their families within minutes, loading up the car and flooding local gas stations as the prepare to leave town.
